headline: Former Ideas Flash Technical Buy Signals. Revisiting 3 Stocks.
summary: Yeti Holdings  a once best-of-breed consumer discretionary name, is making a credible attempt to reclaim that status.  Before this run, Yeti had not logged consecutive weekly advances at any point in 2025.  It followed through last week with a 4.5% gain.
